metadata.name: Cyber City
metadata.description: Cyber ​​City is a bustling city and a city that never sleeps. It is a combination of technology and the crypto world. I have envisioned a city with skyscrapers with a busy environment. This is the city people dream of living in because it has all the facilities and freedom where the hammock is running in a loop and the train shows its colors and people are very happy with the facilities and people can use self generated Ethereum in the lab. Cyber ​​City is the most detailed and well animated from my previous works.
